Enum CefRequest.TransitionType

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<CefRequest.TransitionType>

    CefRequest 

    public static enum CefRequest.TransitionType
extends java.lang.Enum<CefRequest.TransitionType>
    Transition type for a request. Made up of one source value and 0 or more qualifiers.(请求的转换类型。由一个源值和0个或多个限定符组成。)

    • Enum Constant Summary

      TT_AUTO_SUBFRAME

      TT_EXPLICIT

      Source is a "reload" of the page via the Reload function or by re-visiting the same URL.(来源是通过收件箱功能或重新访问同一URL“重新加载”的页面。)

    • Enum Constant Detail

      • TT_AUTO_SUBFRAME

        public static final CefRequest.TransitionType TT_AUTO_SUBFRAME
        Source is a subframe navigation. This is any content that is automatically loaded in a non-toplevel frame. For example, if a page consists of several frames containing ads, those ad URLs will have this transition type. The user may not even realize the content in these pages is a separate frame, so may not care about the URL.(来源是子frame导航。这是在非顶层frame中自动加载的任何内容。例如，如果一个页面由几个包含广告的框架组成，那么这些广告URL将具有这种转换类型。用户甚至可能没有意识到这些页面中的内容是一个单独的frame，因此可能不关心URL。)

      • TT_EXPLICIT

        public static final CefRequest.TransitionType TT_EXPLICIT
        Source is some other "explicit" navigation action such as creating a new browser or using the LoadURL function. This is also the default value for navigations where the actual type is unknown.(来源是其他一些“显式”导航操作，例如创建新浏览器或使用LoadURL函数。这也是实际类型未知的导航的默认值。)

      • TT_FORM_SUBMIT

        public static final CefRequest.TransitionType TT_FORM_SUBMIT
        Source is a form submission by the user. NOTE: In some situations submitting a form does not result in this transition type. This can happen if the form uses a script to submit the contents.(来源是用户提交的表单。注意：在某些情况下，提交表单不会导致这种转换类型。如果表单使用脚本提交内容，就会发生这种情况。)

      • TT_LINK

        public static final CefRequest.TransitionType TT_LINK
        Source is a link click or the JavaScript window.open function. This is also the default value for requests like sub-resource loads that are not navigations.(来源是一个链接点击或JavaScript window.open函数。这也是非导航的子资源加载等请求的默认值。)

      • TT_MANUAL_SUBFRAME

        public static final CefRequest.TransitionType TT_MANUAL_SUBFRAME
        Source is a subframe navigation explicitly requested by the user that will generate new navigation entries in the back/forward list. These are probably more important than frames that were automatically loaded in the background because the user probably cares about the fact that this link was loaded.(来源是用户明确请求的子frame导航，它将在后退/前进列表中生成新的导航条目。这些可能比在后台自动加载的frame更重要，因为用户可能关心加载此链接的事实。)

      • TT_RELOAD

        public static final CefRequest.TransitionType TT_RELOAD
        Source is a "reload" of the page via the Reload function or by re-visiting the same URL. NOTE: This is distinct from the concept of whether a particular load uses "reload semantics" (i.e. bypasses cached data).(来源是通过重新加载功能或重新访问同一URL来“重新加载”页面。注意：这与特定加载是否使用“重载语义”（即绕过缓存数据）的概念不同。)
